# NAME: Social Media and Communities
# AUTHOR: Codex
# UPDATED: 2026-06-14
# FORMAT: Surge Ruleset
# SOURCES: Official service sites, QuixoticHeart/rule-set, blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script, SukkaW/Surge
# NOTE: Major overseas social networks, publishing communities and well-known internet forums.
# NOTE: Standalone messaging services, video platforms, adult/piracy sites, typo domains, generic telemetry, shared cloud ranges and raw IP rules are intentionally excluded.
# NOTE: Federated networks include selected major entry points; arbitrary independent instances cannot be exhaustively represented by a static domain list.

